.TH "nvme_create_ctrl" 9 "nvme_create_ctrl" "July 2025" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_create_ctrl \- Allocate an unconnected NVMe controller
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "nvme_ctrl_t" nvme_create_ctrl
.BI "(nvme_root_t r "  ","
.BI "const char *subsysnqn "  ","
.BI "const char *transport "  ","
.BI "const char *traddr "  ","
.BI "const char *host_traddr "  ","
.BI "const char *host_iface "  ","
.BI "const char *trsvcid "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "r" 12
NVMe root element
.IP "subsysnqn" 12
Subsystem NQN
.IP "transport" 12
Transport type
.IP "traddr" 12
Transport address
.IP "host_traddr" 12
Host transport address
.IP "host_iface" 12
Host interface name
.IP "trsvcid" 12
Transport service ID
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Creates an unconnected controller to be used for \fBnvme_add_ctrl\fP.
.SH "RETURN"
Controller instance
